  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AirIndex
    This class contains information about Air index in station, which ID is stored in field 'id'.
    City
    This class contains information about City of station.
    Commune
    This class contains detailed information about city's commune address.
    DateHandler
    This class changes String to Date, it is sometimes used to compare dates.
    DateHandlerTest  
    Features
    Features class is responsible for whole program logic, it calculates data, draws charts, parse JSON from urls/file, save JSON to files.
    FeaturesTest  
    Main
    Program is using GSON API to downloaad and store JSON files from http://powietrze.gios.gov.pl/pjp/content/api which is Polish governemnt's site monitoring air pollution.
    MeasureData
    This class contains list of MeasureValues objects, containing measures from single sensor.
    MeasureStation  
    MeasureValues
    This class stores information about single measure and date when it was made.
    OptionsParser
    This class Parses arguments from command line, checks their correctnes and use proper functions based on input.
    OptionsParserTest  
    Param
    This class contains information about parameter which can be measured with sensor, it's formula,name and code.
    Sensor
    This class contains information about sensor which measure paramateres value once per hour.
    StIndexLevel
    This class contains information about air index, in field 'indexLevelName' is stored grade of index calculated on station, for instance index may be : good, very bad etc.
    Timetest
    This class is used to test downloading and saving JSON files
